data.description: New Low Price.  Property appraised for $900,000 as is.  Here is your opportunity to own a large end unit Rowe home located  in highly sought-after Petworth! This Completely updated Wardman house is situated a block from Grant circle and is move-in ready.  You will enjoy living in this  spacious home featuring 4 bedrooms and 1 ½ baths, 1st floor sunroom / den, full unfinished basement and large exterior yard with off street parking and 1 car garage.  Lots of Potential and ready for the savvy buyer!   This home is Very Walkable so most errands can be accomplished on foot,  Green Metrorail Green Line at the GEORGIA AVE-PETWORTH, GREEN/YELLOW LINE CENTER PLATFORM stop, Nearby parks include Grant Circle, Sherman Circle and Petworth,  easy access to downtown DC, National Airport, and interstate highways. Additionally, you will be centrally located near shopping, restaurants, libraries, hospitals, and community centers.
